<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-8171] Escaped dollar slashy difference between old and parrot parsers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-8171</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The following test passes with the legacy parser but fails with Parrot&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// legacy parser
&lt;/span&gt;def s1 = $/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; $$/ is an escaped dollar forward slash/$
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; s1 == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; $/ is an escaped dollar forward slash&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// antlr4 enabled (parrot)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;assert&lt;/span&gt; s1 == &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; $/ is an escaped dollar forward slash&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
       |  |
       |  &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt;
       &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt; / is an escaped dollar forward slash
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Noticed this when I inadvertently changed a spec test in commit &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/0fb89906aa587920d11fae063bba1d1f8fe26254&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;0fb89906aa&lt;/a&gt;.  When testing for an escaped dollar slash the test had to be changed (&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/groovy/commit/942cf4eb3e87f2718df490b9e3547f2042720781&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;commit 942cf4eb3e&lt;/a&gt;) to pass using the Antlr4 parser.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Based on the &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.groovy-lang.org/syntax.html#_dollar_slashy_string&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;dollar slashy docs&lt;/a&gt; I am not sure if the old behavior is correct or not.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
